description:
This is a 19 minute workout called '20 Min CALISTHENICS Workout with Beginner Variations | Follow Along' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Try this 20 minute follow along Calisthenics workout that you can do at home with no equipment. I have included scalable exercise options to suit different ability levels.

What is Calisthenics? Calisthenics is bodyweight training using gymnastic movements to develop strength, flexibility, balance and master control over your body.
